s://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B7%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8E%D8%B9%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to go up, ascend, rise"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to rise (of heavenly bodies)","examples":[{"text":"11 Century CE, Wallada bint al-Mustakfi, ترقّب إذا جنّ الظلام زيارتي\nوَبِي مِنْكَ مَا لَوْ كَانَ بِالشَمْسِ لَمْ تَلُحْ ، وَبِالبَدْرِ لَمْ يَطْلُعْ وَبِالنَجْمِ لَمْ يَسْرِ\nwabī minka mā law kāna bi-š-šamsi lam taluḥ , wabi-l-badri lam yaṭluʕ wabi-n-najmi lam yasri\nI feel a love for you that if the light of heaven felt, the sun would not shine, nor the moon rise, nor the stars begin their nightly journey."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to ascend (a mountain, etc.), to mount"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to break forth"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to put forth blossoms"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to come upon, befall"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to surprise"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to observe"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to go, depart"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to visit, reach"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to go out, leave the house, leave the service","tags":["modern"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to originate"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to become"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to occur"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to know, understand"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/tˤa.la.ʕa/","/tˤa.li.ʕa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n26938","headword_ar":"طلّع","root":"TlE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"said of the palm-tree: see 1, former half. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tl~Ehu","text_ar":"طلّعهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taToliyEN","text_ar":"تَطْلِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He put it forth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"produced it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a vulgar word. (TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tl~E kayolahu","text_ar":"طلّع كَيْلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. as above, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He filled his measure."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n26944","headword_ar":"طَلْعٌ","root":"TlE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaloE","text_ar":"طَلْع"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spadix,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spadix in its spathe,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and sometimes, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spathe"},{"kind":"text","text":"alone,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the palm-tree:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O:) the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_igoriyD","text_ar":"اـِغْرِيض"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spadix"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the palm-tree, from over which the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAfuwr","text_ar":"كَافُور"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spathe"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bursts open longitudinally;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flowers of the palm-tree, while in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kAfwr","text_ar":"كافور"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing that comes forth from the palm-tree, as though it were two soles,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sandals, closed together, with the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Himol","text_ar":"حِمْل"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flowers"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"compactly disposed between them, and having the extremity pointed;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vamarap","text_ar":"ثَمَرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"produce"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the palm-tree, in the first stage of its appearance, the covering"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spathe"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of which is called the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kufur~aY","text_ar":"كُفُرَّى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAfuwr","text_ar":"كَافُور"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and what is within this the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_igoriyD","text_ar":"اـِغْرِيض"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"because of its whiteness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) or the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaloE","text_ar":"طَلْع"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what comes forth from the palm-tree and becomes dates if the tree is female; and if the tree is male it does not become dates, but is eaten in its fresh state, or is left upon the palm-tree a certain number of days until there becomes produced in it a white substance like flour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the pollen,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having a strong odour, and with this the female is fecundated;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain white thing that appears from the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kim~","text_ar":"كِمّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spathe"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the palm-tree, to the colour of which"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the teeth are likened, and to the odour thereof"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the sperma:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and also, [sometimes,] the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kim~","text_ar":"كِمّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spathe"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that comes forth from the palm-tree, before it bursts open longitudinally:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and this is also called the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kufur~aY","text_ar":"كُفُرَّى"},{"kind":"text","text":", for] the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaloEu Alkufuz~aY","text_ar":"طَلْعُ الكُفُزَّى"},{"kind":"text","text":"is an instance of the prefixing of a noun to an explicative thereof: (Mgh:) [or this phrase may mean"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the spadix of the spathe of a palm-tree:"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaloEN","text_ar":"طَلْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", it should be added, is sometimes used as a coll. gen. n.: and its n. un. is with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":": thus in explanations of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_igoriyDN","text_ar":"اـِغْرِيضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.] In the Kur xxxvii. 63, it is applied to (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fruit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"produce,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the tree called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alz~aq~uwm","text_ar":"الزَّقُّوم"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the bottom of Hell, metaphorically, because partaking of the form of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TlE","text_ar":"طلع"},{"kind":"text","text":"of dates, or because coming forth from the tree. (Bd.)       -A2-  Also (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miqodaArN","text_ar":"مِقْدَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Number,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quantity"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (K, TA:) so in the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aljayo$u TaloEu A^alofK","text_ar":"الجَيْشُ طَلْعُ اَلْفٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The army consists of the number of a thousand"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K, * TA).       -A3-  See also the next paragraph, in three places."}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","TA","Mgh"]},{"entry_id":"n26945","headword_ar":"طِلْعٌ","root":"TlE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  a subst. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlAiT~ilaAEu","text_ar":"الاِطِّلَاعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": [meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Knowledge:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] whence the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiT~alaEa TiloEa AlEaduw~i","text_ar":"اِطَّلَعَ طِلْعَ العَدُوِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He learned the knowledge of the enemy;"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he obtained knowledge of the state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tidings,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the secret,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the inward,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intrinsic,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"secret, state"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"circumstances, of the enemy"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (S, O, K, TA;) [for]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TiloEa AlEaduw~i","text_ar":"طِلْعَ العَدُوِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xabarahu","text_ar":"خَبَرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sir~ahu","text_ar":"سِرَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (PS,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baATina A^amorihimo","text_ar":"بَاطِنَ اَمْرِهِمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Har p. 82:) and [hence also] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aTolaEotuhu TiloEa A^amoriY","text_ar":"اَطْلَعْتُهُ طِلْعَ اَمْرِى"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I revealed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"showed, to him my secret."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA.)       -A2-  Also (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An elevated place, above what is around it, from which one looks down"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuT~alaEu","text_ar":"يُطَّلَعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the CK erroneously"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuTolaEu","text_ar":"يُطْلَعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]); as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaloEN","text_ar":"طَلْعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K, TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealawotu TiloEa AlA^akamapi","text_ar":"عَلَوْتُ طِلْعَ الاَكَمَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I ascended upon a part of the hill from which I overlooked what was around it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd, O, TA.) ―         -b2-  And (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAHiyapN","text_ar":"نَاحِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A side,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an adjacent tract,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a region,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]; as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaloEN","text_ar":"طَلْعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kuno biTiloEi AlwaAdiY","text_ar":"كُنْ بِطِلْعِ الوَادِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaloEi","text_ar":"طَلْعِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlwAdY","text_ar":"الوادى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biTaloEi AlwAdY","text_ar":"بِطَلْعِ الوادى"},{"kind":"text","text":"also, meaning, as is indicated in the TA, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Be thou in the side,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the valley"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, O:) and one says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN TiloE","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ طِلْع"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlwaAdiY","text_ar":"الوَادِى"},{"kind":"text","text":", without"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"b","text_ar":"ب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is in the side,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the valley"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (O.) ―         -b3-  And (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Any depressed piece of ground:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as has in it a hill:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) [i. e.,] as expl. by As,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any depressed piece of ground having in it a hill from which, when you ascend upon it, you see what is in it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O.)       -A3-  Also the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"serpent:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, O, K:) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Til~N","text_ar":"طِلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","PS","S","O","K","AA"]},{"entry_id":"n26946","headword_ar":"طَلِعٌ","root":"TlE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Desirous, eager,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vehemently eager"},{"kind":"text","text":"]."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nafosN TaliEapN","text_ar":"نَفْسٌ طَلِعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nufuwsN TaliEapN","text_ar":"نُفُوسٌ طَلِعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fariHapN","text_ar":"فَرِحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in form], mean (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A soul,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"souls, desirous, eager,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vehemently eager."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TulaEapN","text_ar":"طُلَعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}